				<wikidot:authorName>insomnimax</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6641498</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Mad scientist uses a reality bender's brain to make an anomalous tea maker? Instant +1</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;minor&nbsp;crit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;close&nbsp;crit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p>initial testing will be initiated in TWO hours.</p> </blockquote> <p>Eh, I don't think this is something that should be here. It kinda messes with the feel of the document, as there is a testing report at the end, (meaning initial testing has already been done).<br /> But overall, I really liked this SCP.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
