						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">sreliops&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Back in the day, Dr. Wilson turned a type green into a perfect tea machine and put it in a secret tea room in his office. When the sublevel got shut down he didn't have a way to move it out without people noticing, so he just sealed the entrance to his secret tea room.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
